{% raw %} 
class DualLoader(Transform):
    def __init__(self, train_path:(str,Path), valid_path:(str,Path)):
        self.train = Path(train_path)
        self.valid = Path(valid_path)
        self.training = True
    def encodes(self, file:(str,Path)):
        folder = self.train if self.training else self.valid
        new_file = random.choice(folder.ls())
        while new_file == file: new_file = random.choice(folder.ls())
        return (file, new_file)
{% endraw %} {% raw %} 
def get_audio_pair_files(file):
    files = get_audio_files(file)
    joins = DualLoader(train_path=fileTrain, valid_path=fileValid)(Tuple(files))
    return [" ".join([str(a),str(b)]) for a,b in joins]

class AudioJoiner(ItemTransform):
    def encodes(self, audios:Tuple):
        print(type(audios[0]))
        return audios[0]+audios[1]
{% endraw %} {% raw %} 
class Split(Transform):
    def encodes(self, files):
        return [tuple(file_pair.split()) for file_pair in files]
{% endraw %} {% raw %} 
class Printer(Transform):
    def encodes(self, x):
        print(type(x))
        return x
